Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.80,0:36:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,英琪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.67,0:36:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.84,0:36:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,英琪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.30,0:36:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,英琪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.30,0:37:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.88,0:37:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你允許的話 我來跟她說
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.34,0:37:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我來解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.30,0:37:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想幫你減輕壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.67,0:37:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你允許的話
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.88,0:37:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.55,0:37:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.80,0:38:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.96,0:38:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是阿雅老師
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.96,0:38:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我想告訴你我是英琪的合法丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.67,0:38:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我們已經結婚了 還有
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.51,0:38:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.51,0:38:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-銀?\N-銀?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.55,0:38:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-銀 你還好嗎?\N-看吧 我就說不要
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.63,0:38:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.71,0:38:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.55,0:38:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 我頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.13,0:38:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,都會好的 英琪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.51,0:38:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.53,0:38:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,生活本來是我想的那麼美
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.85,0:39:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,直到你來打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.94,0:39:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,最初沒有錯誤 沒有矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.40,0:39:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,直到你來破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.19,0:39:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.94,0:39:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可我的心選擇愛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.25,0:39:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要我遠離
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.62,0:39:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,刪掉你的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.95,0:39:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但生活卻把我和你
